<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Plants sprout following disturbances, such as fire and cutting (Howard 1992d), though the history of fires in this alliance is not well known. Stands in the subalpine portions of the state are not fire prone and experience natural disturbances, such as snow inundation and minor rock falls.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
			<td>Medium (5-50 years)
				
			</td>
		</tr>
		
